{"tid":1940830,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"車主對於返廠check有乜睇法","createTime":"2020-03-24T04:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T11:45:26.000Z","uid":320245,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a4675528bb64622199f368b33ab9727afc9e42db","tid":1940830,"uid":320245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"對於有揸車的人都知道，車要定期做換油保養嗰啲。而買新車既都知，要定期返廠check先至有得Warranty。唔知咁多位覺得攞部車返廠搞係畀貴D但係人地專業有相應service<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，定係覺得名過其實無奸不商，間間都咁上下有邊間唔係亂咁來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。歡迎討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c33781ad92282c62323153dededdf4f6b1ab515","tid":1940830,"uid":196924,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:57:12.000Z","msg":"專條撚<br />\n年年都有人投訴返完廠多咗兩條痕<br />\n尤其係某啲牌子"},{"pid":"e0c751711073b100518a5c6d3d983714aed0de13","tid":1940830,"uid":316473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"貴"},{"pid":"8adecca587ce8e1b195d7b56f82bbe28d8aec156","tid":1940830,"uid":37107,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:41:10.000Z","msg":"到而家都唔明架車既warranty有乜用 有咩事搵車房搞仲平<br />\n冷門車例外"},{"pid":"dd9cb52fb6036b34e7c3aa98bedbfe36f09e8a4a","tid":1940830,"uid":119610,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:50:25.000Z","msg":"公司部貨車返原廠檢查完無耐著engine 燈，然後發現就快無晒偈油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d679aa85a88455effa76ebc8e2bb362c68a30f","tid":1940830,"uid":67116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T09:58:19.000Z","msg":"交保護費<br />\n保養係呃9人，無保護費就吃屎"},{"pid":"d5141c065dc6ac333fca3dfd48b49f19aef73d25","tid":1940830,"uid":79410,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:48:44.000Z","msg":"保養唔知保乜. 整乜都收你錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2804b761df9abc5dcc684b334b054ebefb21e51b","tid":1940830,"uid":3937,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:11:36.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n香港所謂既「保養」包咩<br />\n咩都要另外俾錢<br />\n<br />\n外國又係點？"},{"pid":"9e5a6a8f0b952d88bd36838c20743bbce9009d37","tid":1940830,"uid":233593,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:39:15.000Z","msg":"番原廠做一次service 就跟住個表剔有咩項目check左，做完話番俾你聽架車有咩問題<br />\n出街車房換一次油就你話番俾佢聽換油之外有咩問題要跟<br />\n要考慮依個問題嘅講到尾都係錢字<br />\n<br />\n伸利：有車"},{"pid":"019dc5cde10b669710bd9b26c7e107cfd602dcf8","tid":1940830,"uid":129474,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:07:51.000Z","msg":"用例子答<br />\n六年前買行貨noah，每年要返一次廠檢查，唔返就斷保養，每次換油加檢查三千幾落樓，已經係最低消費，不過買得行車基本上都唔計較呢啲，唯一r頭嘅係新車落地半年比人隊pat，返廠報價，完全感受唔到所謂「保養」可以帶嚟咩好處，要成個尾門換，8萬，好彩有全保。<br />\n<br />\n最近換車，直接買水貨算，反正原廠所謂維修「有信心」外，基本上只要有間相熟車房已經可以完全抵消<br />\n<br />\n當然上述只限皇冠，其他廠唔知"},{"pid":"39230c0bf83b9ae3e2c7058b2b8c5c2f640ebafd","tid":1940830,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2804b761df9abc5dcc684b334b054ebefb21e51b","tid":1940830,"uid":3937,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:11:36.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n香港所謂既「保養」包咩<br />\n咩都要另外俾錢<br />\n<br />\n外國又係點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:09:40.000Z","msg":"主要係波箱引擎，保護期內冧咗要幫你換"},{"pid":"3ab9a6b162a73d4c9465c18636d6c35e12f7a294","tid":1940830,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:11:26.000Z","msg":"1000 , 10000 跟住唔返"},{"pid":"7f6b0f2ffd9383e0f147ba3c8d3ed415b3831ce4","tid":1940830,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ab9a6b162a73d4c9465c18636d6c35e12f7a294","tid":1940830,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:11:26.000Z","msg":"1000 , 10000 跟住唔返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:32:05.000Z","msg":"思路正確"},{"pid":"4f9394fec8f3919d2ba9f1677a108276c5a3ad6d","tid":1940830,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"掃把佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通換偈油出去比人搞<br />\n但佢副cvt就麻乜煩..冧左大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n換完油要reset電腦出面無乜車房識搞<br />\n換波箱油就會返廠"},{"pid":"0cacdf69fd5fa6ee8b8961186c4a431ed706ad5b","tid":1940830,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:53:17.000Z","msg":"我揸26新車, 保養只係要比偈油錢, 就算有野壞要換都只係要比料錢唔洗人工<br />\n不過只保到8000公里"},{"pid":"52d2aa1a097e22b8738f49cf14591edb451a2b65","tid":1940830,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f9394fec8f3919d2ba9f1677a108276c5a3ad6d","tid":1940830,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"掃把佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通換偈油出去比人搞<br />\n但佢副cvt就麻乜煩..冧左大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n換完油要reset電腦出面無乜車房識搞<br />\n換波箱油就會返廠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:57:16.000Z","msg":"加多d 電子野 搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實都係咁個制"},{"pid":"685bf3492b4307cdf021ba4ed3dbcb0ae5eb0671","tid":1940830,"uid":132945,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:00:36.000Z","msg":"幾年前買過部Audi , 全新大昌香港行<br />\nKeep住返原廠做保養、每次大概五六千<br />\n我揸得多，日日揸返工，一年大概返廠兩次<br />\n一年半之後發覺呔盤轉向有問題<br />\n檢查完之後發現呔箱問題<br />\n要由德國全set 訂返嚟<br />\n因為我有keep 住返原廠交陀地<br />\n所以今次零件、維修費用全免<br />\n<br />\n後來我查詢返，全組零件連運費要5萬幾<br />\n自此以後 我都會keep住交陀地直至保養期完<br />\n<br />\n利申： 出過四架全新車 （一架日本、三架歐洲）"},{"pid":"7055b2244fcc616f9be0a005ddd33771b8e86032","tid":1940830,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:05:38.000Z","msg":"老虎架雀士換咗大面版，所以中控台換咗，有次check 完車兼換氣袋零件，收車塊中控台膠板裂咗，屌佢老母話唔關佢事，又話香港行貨冇呢款，冇得整又話唔會賠，送返次check 車保數，大昌你含啦"},{"pid":"dc86f7d40278b9a96c2ab4c5ab3bb3365a7b5ed3","tid":1940830,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2804b761df9abc5dcc684b334b054ebefb21e51b